Aimed at empowering fashion lovers to participate in the circular fashion movement, the brand partnership between Pomellato and @vestiaireco offers customers an opportunity to extend the lifespan of pre-loved Pomellato jewels and start a new love affair with this season’s collection. 
To further support the circular fashion and sustainability commitment, Pomellato and Vestiaire Collective team up with @hannalhoumeau #Pomellato #VestiaireCollective

Pomellato partners with @vestiaireco to empower the circular fashion movement. 
Launching just before Valentine’s Day, the partnership celebrates a woman’s love affair with her jewellery and aligns a joint commitment to driving sustainability and circularity in the fashion industry and consumer mind-set.
To further celebrate, Pomellato and Vestiaire Collective team up with jewellery lover @thomsenmichaela
